620
00:40:52,616 --> 00:40:56,416
And she falls asleep.
Which, she would be sleepy.

621
00:40:56,787 --> 00:40:57,879
Can you go back?

622
00:40:57,955 --> 00:40:59,820
See if anybody spoke with her
before she acted up.

623
