to enormous trouble
to find your little friend.

636
00:41:48,606 --> 00:41:50,574
And found her, they have.

637
00:41:52,109 --> 00:41:54,600
Do you all know
what it is you're carrying?

638
00:42:02,419 --> 00:42:03,943
