639
00:42:05,322 --> 00:42:08,382
I'm sorry.
They should be.

640
00:42:09,627 --> 00:42:13,119
But I'll show them. Oh, God.

641
00:42:14,632 --> 00:42:17,726
It's okay. Hey, it's okay.

642
00:42:19,069 --> 00:42:21,264
Show me off like a dog.

643
00:42:22,473 --> 00:42:23,963
Old men covered in blood.

644
00:42:24,041 --> 00:42:26,839
It never touched them,
but they're drowning in it.

645
00:42:28,412 --> 00:42:31,677
I don't know what I'm saying.
I never know what I'm saying.

646
00:42:34,818 --> 00:42:37,082
In the Maidenhead,
you said something.

647
00:42:38,122 --> 00:42:40,420
When you were triggered,
do you remember?

648
00:42:40,491 --> 00:42:43,119
The Captain saw you
say something on the feed.

649
00:42:44,862 --> 00:42:46,159
Miranda.

650
00:42:47,765 --> 00:42:48,754
Miranda.

651
00:42:50,668 --> 00:42:52,329
Ask her.

652
00:42:54,405 --> 00:42:56,168
