654
00:43:06,617 --> 00:43:07,606
No.

655
00:43:09,520 --> 00:43:10,578
Not right.

656
00:43:13,457 --> 00:43:17,416
But I think
when they triggered you...

657
00:43:18,262 --> 00:43:20,230
it somehow brought this up.

658
00:43:20,764 --> 00:43:22,857
This memory.
It isn't mine.

659
00:43:23,200 --> 00:43:24,861
The memory, it isn't mine.

660
00:43:24,935 --> 00:43:27,836
And I shouldn't have
to carry it. It isn't mine.

661
00:43:28,138 --> 00:43:30,504
Don't make me sleep again.
I won't.

662
00:43:31,375 --> 00:43:32,364
I won't.

663
00:43:33,143 --> 00:43:34,667
